#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.103"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.103:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.103:0.2"
msgid "11. Samaṇasaññāvagga"
msgstr "11. Perceptions for Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.103:0.3"
msgid "103. Micchattasutta"
msgstr "103. The Wrong Way"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.212"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.103:1.1"
msgid "“Micchattaṃ, bhikkhave, āgamma virādhanā hoti, no ārādhanā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, relying on the wrong way leads to failure, not success."

msgctxt "an10.103:1.2"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, micchattaṃ āgamma virādhanā hoti, no ārādhanā?"
msgstr "And how does relying on the wrong way lead to failure, not success?"

#. VAR: micchāñāṇissa → micchāñāṇassa (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an10.103:1.3"
msgid ""
"Micchādiṭṭhikassa, bhikkhave, micchāsaṅkappo pahoti, micchāsaṅkappassa "
"micchāvācā pahoti, micchāvācassa micchākammanto pahoti, micchākammantassa "
"micchāājīvo pahoti, micchāājīvassa micchāvāyāmo pahoti, micchāvāyāmassa "
"micchāsati pahoti, micchāsatissa micchāsamādhi pahoti, micchāsamādhissa "
"micchāñāṇaṃ pahoti, micchāñāṇissa micchāvimutti pahoti."
msgstr ""
"Wrong view gives rise to wrong thought. Wrong thought gives rise to wrong "
"speech. Wrong speech gives rise to wrong action. Wrong action gives rise to "
"wrong livelihood. Wrong livelihood gives rise to wrong effort. Wrong effort "
"gives rise to wrong mindfulness. Wrong mindfulness gives rise to wrong "
"immersion. Wrong immersion gives rise to wrong knowledge. Wrong knowledge "
"gives rise to wrong freedom."

msgctxt "an10.103:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, micchattaṃ āgamma virādhanā hoti, no ārādhanā."
msgstr "That’s how relying on the wrong way leads to failure, not success."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.103:2.1"
msgid "Sammattaṃ, bhikkhave, āgamma ārādhanā hoti, no virādhanā."
msgstr "Relying on the right way leads to success, not failure."

msgctxt "an10.103:2.2"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, sammattaṃ āgamma ārādhanā hoti, no virādhanā?"
msgstr "And how does relying on the right way lead to success, not failure?"

#. VAR: sammāñāṇissa → sammāñāṇassa (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an10.103:2.3"
msgid ""
"Sammādiṭṭhikassa, bhikkhave, sammāsaṅkappo pahoti, sammāsaṅkappassa "
"sammāvācā pahoti, sammāvācassa sammākammanto pahoti, sammākammantassa "
"sammāājīvo pahoti, sammāājīvassa sammāvāyāmo pahoti, sammāvāyāmassa "
"sammāsati pahoti, sammāsatissa sammāsamādhi pahoti, sammāsamādhissa "
"sammāñāṇaṃ pahoti, sammāñāṇissa sammāvimutti pahoti."
msgstr ""
"Right view gives rise to right thought. Right thought gives rise to right "
"speech. Right speech gives rise to right action. Right action gives rise to "
"right livelihood. Right livelihood gives rise to right effort. Right effort "
"gives rise to right mindfulness. Right mindfulness gives rise to right "
"immersion. Right immersion gives rise to right knowledge. Right knowledge "
"gives rise to right freedom."

msgctxt "an10.103:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sammattaṃ āgamma ārādhanā hoti, no virādhanā”ti."
msgstr "That’s how relying on the right way leads to success, not failure.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.103:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
